{"tid":183520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我晏晝只係食魚柳包，食咗成年啦！","createTime":"2017-04-02T07:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T07:06:32.000Z","uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67cfcd05e1b48a2fcfbde7c5ceb8f74d45a9380c","tid":183520,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T07:05:32.000Z","msg":"每日6點就起身睇新聞、食早餐，然後返工，之後一直做做做到7點，我晏晝只係食魚柳包，食咗成年啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢都每日早上六時起床看報紙、吃早餐，然後九時上班，之後便一直工作至晚上七時，「我晏晝只係食魚柳包，食成年啦！<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20050219/4676948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20050219%2F4676948&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=1c3defdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20050219%2F4676948&h=ff24d4af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20050219/4676948</a>"},{"pid":"ba61d0a4eea294161844e2a69ad79326fac62184","tid":183520,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T07:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}